{
  "stem": "22889.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had to go to the latrine to wash up, go to the bathroom, whatever it be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the latrine were the big speakers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All around were a bunch of maybe around 50 speakers, big, huge speakers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the water was coming, cold water, naturally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no soap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just wash your face.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had a pair of pants-- no underpants-- jacket, and a shirt and go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was no sit down-- was a bathroom was a piece of board.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [LAUGHS] It was a big hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then you-- whatever had to be done, you did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no paper to wipe yourself, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When you're a slave, you're a slave, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then back to the barracks. 6 o'clock in the morning, we were getting our ration-- a slice of bread, like a toast bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Black bread made out of sawdust and cornmeal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a coffee, black coffee, if you want to call it coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Many times, sometime when things were good for the German, like for Christmastime or something, like some kind of holidays, used to get a piece of margarine, a piece of jello, something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For Christmas I remember I used to get a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You had choice to get two cigarette or sniff tobacco.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I used to get the-- I like sniff tobacco because last longer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I used to take a piece of cement paper, spit them on them and sprinkle and roll them and smoke them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's what I like better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We used to get-- then when we used to get up, got our breakfast, then we're to go to the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were divided into groups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everybody knew where to go already.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
